{
  "stem": "1415.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I assumed because they were adults that that's OK.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the people that saw me there, you know, they weren't very happy to see a child because it means that their-- their life was jeopardized.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was not very welcomed either way because [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] amongst-- amongst the people in the camp, children were not welcome because, first of all, a lot of people were angry their children were not there.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A lot of people were angry because I jeopardized their lives.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And a lot of people maybe would have liked to have helped me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But most of them, I-- I presented a terrible threat, terrible threat being there, next to them, at any time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- I wasn't very welcomed by-- by my own people either at that-- in those years.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was very difficult [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to survive as a child because I didn't know anything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only thing I knew is that if my mother is there, my father is there, that must be OK.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then I'm safe.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then I'm OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because my brothers are there, my father is there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then it must be fine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I tried to tell my mother not to-- when she pulled me in, I said no, he knows, he knows, he knows I'm here.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I guess she didn't hear me, or-- or-- it happened so fast.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, this incident happened so fast.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm telling it slowly, but it happened very fast.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was just amongst the few times that I came face to face [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] with-- with death.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the only thing I could think of is wanting to see my parents.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nothing else.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
